node.accessibility_caption: Photo by fuck the bourgeoisie☭ in UNGA with @the.decadent.socialist. May be an image of text.

node.text:
gonna start using “No🇺🇸🇮🇱” instead of “No❤️”
.
fun fact this is the 29th time the UNGA resolves to call for the end to sanctions— the US has never had more than four votes on its side (including itself and israel every time ofc). even protofascist brazil abstained this time after supporting the US during the last vote
.
also it is worth repeating that the existence of sanctions does not delegitimize the protests or the cuban voices struggling to break through the black-and-white perspective that westerners —left and right— are bent on force onto them
.
“The Cuban Hustle” by Sujatha Fernandes is a great and short read for anyone interested in bringing some nuanced thinking to the conversation
.
#seized from @the.decadent.socialist
